<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      /* Email styles need to be inline */
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1>WaveWise says "Thanks!"</h1>
    <p> <%= "#{@name}" %>, </p>
    <p>Thank you for submitting a new surf spot!</p> 
    <p>Your information is used to add a new spot to our service and help surfers find the absolute best waves right now.</p>
    <p><%= "#{@spot}" %> will be added to our service after we have had a chance to check the surf conditions.</p>
    <p>The team at WaveWise appreciates you contribution to the surf community!</p>
    <%= yield %>
  </body>
</html>

